{"tid":848038,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【赤色恐怖】理大學生會強烈譴責校方撕走及用鮮紅紙遮蓋民主牆上「連儂牆」","createTime":"2018-10-04T15:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T09:15:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6271d052a2e9b20de43632477cd3d2034b70b00f","tid":848038,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T15:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/MGpM8ytP/POLYU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FMGpM8ytP%2FPOLYU.jpg&h=ad537f61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n理工大學學生會不滿校方要求，還原他們早前臨時更改的民主牆守則、撕走及以紅紙遮蓋學生會在民主牆上建立的「連儂牆」，對事件予以強烈譴責。<br />\n<br />\n理大學生會會長林穎恒指，早前已就事件向校方發聲明要求高層人員限時內回應，但校方未有理會，學生會部分成員於是在今午直接到大學管理層的辦公樓層要求對話，但最後只獲回應稱本星期六高層與學生會會面時才討論，質疑為何無即時答案及不肯向傳媒回應。<br />\n<br />\n林穎恒表示，學生會不會出席周六的會議，認為校方高層無心與他們討論，又稱若校方再不回應，會在該校本星期六的資訊日上有進一步行動。"},{"pid":"b91b719a070ffd1b5ded848f463d2e80b0ec29e9","tid":848038,"uid":93043,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T15:44:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53de35d879140a6168c96ff75570df7308c3fc51","tid":848038,"uid":93043,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T15:44:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c799768d822d009f5cbeb390eea71eb06c0041d","tid":848038,"uid":93043,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T15:45:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36af35488f3418809f67faac264a5b8c9c01adad","tid":848038,"uid":66527,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T16:26:07.000Z","msg":"係張紅紙上面寫香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6292c2867270f47d2eead7a7efaa40d06885eeb","tid":848038,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36af35488f3418809f67faac264a5b8c9c01adad","tid":848038,"uid":66527,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T16:26:07.000Z","msg":"係張紅紙上面寫香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-